      "content": "thanks. the problem is that i'm working on bare metal hardware and i can't really run valgrind or any of those heavy tools on the actual target chip. it's a very constrained environment. what can i do for manual instrumentation or better ways to monitor the heap usage without a full profiler? maybe something like custom wrappers for malloc/free?",
